summary: Add my personal character as a preset for you !
descriptionHtml:
I wanted to share my preset for a nord style female character, it's purely narcissistic ! :P

[color=#ff0000][size=5][b]ECE preset V2 released ![/b] Hope you'll find it better.
[/size][/color]
[size=4]It might be possible to turn my presets into followers through [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54509/?]Familiar Faces[/url] mod by Verteiron if you want to ! [/size]

[b]Required / recommended mods[/b] (for the same result) :

- [url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url] 
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] by expired6978
- SG Hair Pack 268 by HelloSanta
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The eyes of beauty[/url]  (Elves Edition) by LogRaam
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20483/?@]Women of Skyrim - enhanced female normalmaps[/url] by zzjay
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32986/?]Mature skin textures V2 Beta[/url] by Maevan2
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34346/?]Smile in HD[/url] by zzjay
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34539/?]Battle hardened warpaints[/url] by Diethardt 
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url] by tetrodoxin 

[b]Installation[/b] : 

- Simply download the file manually
- Extract the "8.slot"
- Place it in your Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
- In game, open RaceMenu, go to Presets tab and select the 8th slot (I chose 8 to be quite sure to not overwrite your other presets)
- Enjoy ! 

Screenshot with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23812/?]Seasons of Skyrim[/url].

PS : Feel free to share your own screenshots for my pleasure ! x)

PS2 : If you like, I will create a personal preset for each non beast race. =)

Quorr.
author: Quorr
